2016", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC7733.html", target="_top", tooltip="The purpose of this document is to provide guidance in the selection and use of protocols from the Routing Protocol for Low-Power and Lossy Networks (RPL) protocol suite to implement the features required for control in building and home environments."];
