  RFC8025 [label="RFC8025
IPv6 over Low-Power Wireless Personal
Area Network (6LoWPAN) Paging Dispatch
2016", shape=ellipse, URL="RFC8025.html", target="_top", tooltip="This specification updates RFC 4944 to introduce a new context switch mechanism for IPv6 over Low-Power Wireless Personal Area Network (6LoWPAN) compression, expressed in terms of Pages and signaled by a new Paging Dispatch."];
